init_text:
What Stereotypical Characters Make You Cringe?

What stereotypical characters in books, movies or television shows make you cringe and why? Would you ever not watch or read something because of its offensive portrayal of someone?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is not to say that white men should not play important roles in entertainment; it is more to show that women, African Americans and other races are

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is imperative that Hollywood and the entertainment industry start to change their perspective on what makes a good leading character.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If not, people will feel like Hollywood is not representing them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If Hollywood wants to stay in business it needs to move away from stereotypes and embrace film making that appeals to all groups.
